{"tid":1509724,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"和理非必須再進化支援真勇武","createTime":"2019-08-27T02:44:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T07:55:33.000Z","uid":114487,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"788aab95b5567f4f042f8408142f77b99c1ede00","tid":1509724,"uid":114487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T02:44:13.000Z","msg":"頭盔先, 01post 但係777 啱啱個記者會基本上align 下面ge 分析/風向<br />\n<br />\n個人睇法係 和理非必須要再進化成勇武, 唔落手打都要做消防隊/救人隊, 勇武兵力有限 必須由和理非補給 <br />\n<br />\n//據掌握港府想法的建制派消息指，政府高層研判，現階段一旦答允成立獨立調查委員會，會重挫警隊士氣，更難收拾目前「野貓式」暴力示威行動，故不可能答允，但若只回應一、兩項訴求，如正式宣布撤回修例，示威者又不會就此罷休收手，故衡量後認為一動不如一靜，短期內都不會回應五大訴求，反而會與示威者打「消耗戰」，每次衝突拘捕激進示威者，「拉得幾多得幾多」，「拉到無人為止」。//<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/368236/%E6%94%BF%E5%9C%88%E9%A2%A8%E8%81%B2-%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E4%B8%8D%E6%9C%83%E7%AD%94%E5%85%81%E4%BA%94%E5%A4%A7%E8%A8%B4%E6%B1%82-%E6%B6%88%E8%80%97%E6%88%B0-%E6%8A%97%E8%A1%A1%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=mama\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%2583%2585%2F368236%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%259C%2588%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E8%2581%25B2-%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%2581%25AF-%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%259C%2583%25E7%25AD%2594%25E5%2585%2581%25E4%25BA%2594%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E6%25B1%2582-%25E6%25B6%2588%25E8%2580%2597%25E6%2588%25B0-%25E6%258A%2597%25E8%25A1%25A1%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%3Futm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_source%3Dfbpost_link%26utm_campaign%3Dmama&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrlQYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=2a273dd6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/368236/%E6%94%BF%E5%9C%88%E9%A2%A8%E8%81%B2-%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E4%B8%8D%E6%9C%83%E7%AD%94%E5%85%81%E4%BA%94%E5%A4%A7%E8%A8%B4%E6%B1%82-%E6%B6%88%E8%80%97%E6%88%B0-%E6%8A%97%E8%A1%A1%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp